                    maximum 25 children. Guest limit 35 (includes both children and parents)
                </p>
                <p>
                    $100 deposit: $50 to hold date and $50 security desposit.<br></br>
                    Balance due before party begins.
                </p>
                <h1>Scheduling:</h1>
                <p>Party times are 10:00 a.m., 1:00 p.m. and 4:00 p.m. on Saturdays.<br></br>
                    Fridays 4:00 p.m. only.
                </p>
  </div>

  <div class="right">
    <h2><Image src={'../static/party/1.png'} sx={{width: ['400px', '400px']}} padding="20px"/></h2>
    <Box>
      <ColoredCard cardwidth="400px" cardcolor="orange" fontSize="14px" line1text="CALL US" line2text="281-259-0039"></ColoredCard>
      <br></br>
      <ColoredCard cardwidth={400} cardheight={5/6} lettersize1= "80%" cardcolor="orange" line1text="EMAIL US" line2text="ftwl.education@gmail.com"></ColoredCard>
    </Box>
  </div>

  </div>
  <Box width={1 / 5}></Box>
  </Flex>

